reviewText: Betty White and the ladies have wonderful chemistry together. Though this season does not have the consistency of previous seasons there are still enough funny moments to make this great viewing. Appearances by Carol Burnett and the ladies from Mary Tyler Moore Show are particularly noteworthy.
Title: Hot in Cleveland: Season 4

reviewText: Betty White steals the show on Hot in Cleveland!  It is full of laughs and definitely one of my favorite shows on TV!  Added bonus is that they make fun of Cleveland all the time, which having lived there and hated it, I love!
Title: Hot in Cleveland: Season 4

reviewText: Betty White is the best! This series gets better and better each season. I can't wait for Season 5 in the spring! It's gonna be awesome!!
Title: Hot in Cleveland: Season 4

reviewText: Classic cast, this is so fresh compared to every other TV series. This has a strong cast and great guest stars that add to the shows. Some of the shows are very touching and others make you laugh out loud.
